{"tid":1329443,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求設立隔夜熱門台","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:41:45.000Z","uid":73392,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a63a38a92de0474f9a59f78afc847f507099abbf","tid":1329443,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"連登一去到凌晨，根本就唔係連登，而係五毛登，成班135毛，瘋狂開post，瘋狂推垃圾post，大量刷正負評，一起身個個熱門post都係135毛開嘅，根本凌晨時份嘅連登，唔係一個討論區，而係一班收左錢嘅人，9叫嘅洗版區，嚴重違反左討論區應有嘅討論功能<br />\n<br />\n故此強烈建議，應限制凌晨時份開post，推post嘅次數<br />\n<br />\n或者該時段開嘅post，同推嘅post，要有200留言加2000正負評數，才可以上熱門<br />\n<br />\n又或者設立，凌晨熱門台，將所有凌晨至上熱門嘅post歸類為凌晨熱門，令大眾係區分資訊時，多一個參考<br />\n<br />\n求連仔接納建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fbd27f0fd38020788da34361e86d5d95785563","tid":1329443,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd499f1d64eeb9e6fa23fadb94faab28b08d1af0","tid":1329443,"uid":3631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"491a79ff0dd2b492007d02aee7188b44feb9bbb1","tid":1329443,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1344224f72ae80ed2217c20bd16897b9fdad7bcf","tid":1329443,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40be5c8f14bc618bfed9766ff1fb30093732c3be","tid":1329443,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"或者可以改一下個algorithm, devalue midnight 嘅interaction?"},{"pid":"ef8cb6c967628878ed5e52993be3f7e9ff980691","tid":1329443,"uid":114937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0